verbose_text: In addition to identifying PfPKA as a parasite Rab5A- and Rab7-effector protein, our study suggests a possible role for cAMP dependent protein kinase activity in regulating PfRab5A- and PfRab7 mediated vesicular transport in malaria parasites.
evidence: cAMP-dependent protein kinase activity in regulating PfRab5A- and PfRab7-mediated vesicular transport
